{"tid":1287524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解台灣可以聲援香港，香港唔可以聲援武漢","createTime":"2019-07-05T08:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T09:24:16.000Z","uid":85612,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4353f817f0b84a3ec791ec464f83b9e56b427c81","tid":1287524,"uid":85612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:50:06.000Z","msg":"size=6]<span style=\"color: red;\">咁係因為武漢人都唔想畀你聲援啊on9! 做咩要枉作好人</span>[/size=6]<br />\n<br />\n台灣咁多人聲援港人，或多或少係佢地都要用挑起民眾嘅反共情緒，嚟拉抬蔡英文等綠營政治人物嘅選情<br />\n港台反中人士，互相利用，好明顯係雙贏嘅<br />\n<br />\n而家你班香港人去支持武漢班大陸人搞事，對本地政治有咩好處？只會模糊運動焦點。<br />\n退一萬步，香港人聲援對武漢人有咩好處？人地唔係搞民運，人地搞環保架咋，九五搭八。<br />\n<br />\n外國勢力支持你，係因為香港係大陸嘅金融中心，有相當經濟價值，外國人介入，係以一國兩制，高度自治，港人治港依幾個大原則為前提。外商都係想有錢齊齊齊搵，廢事畀大陸政府搞串個party，外國政府就想打香港牌，用嚟反制中共政府。無人，我重申，無人想香港變成反共民主地，咁樣唔符合所有外部勢力嘅利益，亦唔符合我地嘅自我定位同能力。<br />\n<br />\n再者，對於想加強香港人身分認同嘅連登仔嚟講，台灣罷工你可以支持，蘇丹你可以支持，惟獨係對於中國事務，你一支持就有機會形塑共感共情。想高度自治，就要切離愛國幼稚病，堅決抵制任何有助促進愛國情操嘅運動。香港人愈愛國，愈唔會有自治、民主同自由，依樣係定律嚟。"},{"pid":"19b5ee045c12f164546d0324703b3c7f45384404","tid":1287524,"uid":200758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:50:25.000Z","msg":"五毛可以用武漢分化我地，我地都可以利用武漢將把火燒上大陸，但記住唔係幫武漢，77當日要集中係五大訴求先<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJfWtfJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJfWtfJ.jpg&h=3b2d02f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r6QrQt4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr6QrQt4.jpg&h=02ad2ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LvSJXSZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLvSJXSZ.png&h=0386e4d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ofWuem.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ofWuem.png&h=f545a766&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad49227654f69c5896aa2de2a18bfb4e68873e80","tid":1287524,"uid":127569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:52:18.000Z","msg":"台灣香港都係反共反支，但支那人邊忽係同路人啊，攞來比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44daf93b1c22489b04acd23d5fa3e4053d531649","tid":1287524,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T08:55:29.000Z","msg":"因為台灣而家得閒 冇燃眉之急<br />\n加上香港有國際地位 幫香港出聲可以突顯台灣既國際地位 表達自己異於支那<br />\n<br />\n但係香港都燒到埋身都仲要理人<br />\n仲要理個冇國際地位又唔係有港資既中國城市<br />\n除左為左攪到香港人錯誤表達自己都係支那人之外<br />\n諗唔到原因"},{"pid":"57d3802922b5d64aa59442be24f572b202fbf012","tid":1287524,"uid":270179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:01:02.000Z","msg":"唔好俾人分化到<br />\n冇人話要反攻大陸<br />\n只係要燒佢後欄<br />\n不割席<br />\n不篤灰<br />\n兄弟爬山，各有各做，互相支援<br />\n（唔妥武漢就印多幾千張五大訴求瘋狂派，唔駛係連登當對方係仇人咁屌）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n1.撤回條例<br />\n2.釋放義士<br />\n3.取消暴動定性<br />\n4.追究警方濫用武力鎮壓<br />\n5.落實雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JhUkfM8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJhUkfM8.jpg&h=e0e1744e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGPPTyO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGPPTyO.jpg&h=38fb36f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ALdQC0u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FALdQC0u.png&h=feca3407&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HtoEwdk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHtoEwdk.png&h=45ccf763&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Np0Z6F.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Np0Z6F.png&h=d451cb32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/05/145107_1568e89c3160c354acbc9eda8c078eee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F05%2F145107_1568e89c3160c354acbc9eda8c078eee.png&h=2adf7012&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80f8656f251756f43392f05345dac35024d62d10","tid":1287524,"uid":250082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:16:07.000Z","msg":"唔需要聲援武漢唔需要聲援武漢,因為武漢人只當你係港獨反動分子而唔係自己人"},{"pid":"7e1a20a61b6b94dbc1ba20bb3937dd29cf4999f0","tid":1287524,"uid":125809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80f8656f251756f43392f05345dac35024d62d10","tid":1287524,"uid":250082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:16:07.000Z","msg":"唔需要聲援武漢唔需要聲援武漢,因為武漢人只當你係港獨反動分子而唔係自己人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"078f0d7f82a9348d76aaafcc96bddf83fcb5be72","tid":1287524,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T09:24:16.000Z","msg":"又係呢啲垃圾標題<br />\n豬隊友屌極都有"}]}